{"url": "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/films/2018/02/02/bill-ted-star-alex-winter-tells-hellish-sexual-abuse-child-actor/", "text": "Bill and Ted star Alex Winter has said he suffered \"hellish\" sexual abuse as a child actor in the Seventies, by an older man who is now dead, and became \"very dysfunctional\" while dealing with his trauma.\n\nWinter, 52, is best known for playing high school Bill S Preston in the Bill and Ted comedy film franchise with Keanu Reeves.\n\nHe told BBC Radio 5 Live that making the Bill and Ted films was a \"therapeutic\" experience. \"It was really, really helpful for me mentally,\" he said. \"The world of Bill and Ted is a very sweet and fun place to run around in.\"\n\nWinter continued: \"Keanu and I were close. The director [Stephen Herek] and all of us were close... we all very young, we all had each other\u2019s backs. It was a very safe, familial environment.\"\n\nBefore appearing in 1989 hit Bill and Ted's Excellent Adventure, Winter had his breakthrough role as a young actor in horror comedy The Lost Boys (1987), alongside Corey Feldman. Feldman has also spoken about his traumatic experiences as a child actor, and recently claimed to have been sexually abused while working on The Lost Boys.", "images": ["https://www.telegraph.co.uk/etc.clientlibs/settings/wcm/designs/telegraph/core/clientlibs/ui/dist/static/resources/images/flags/USA-SVG.svg", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/films/2025/11/17/TELEMMGLPICT000448857153_17634021894840_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqMWdsSKKvzw-FGx9TwBukTJyJlaCk9qVjq_Od9p9TOrk.jpeg?imwidth=350", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/briefs/2025/11/17/TELEMMGLPICT000449461268_176338766262417_trans_NvBQzQNjv4Bq8Qp0pNHexMOErsxHSFiWCFxkQAzM52rCQi79C5zToXo.jpeg?imwidth=350", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/etc.clientlibs/settings/wcm/designs/telegraph/core/clientlibs/ui/dist/static/resources/images/flags/UK-SVG.svg", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/news/2025/11/11/TELEMMGLPICT000438287554_17628762780190_